         <div type="translation">
            <ab>
               <supplied reason="explanation">This is the</supplied> tomb of <seg cert="low">Jordanes</seg> from the stem of
Eulalios, whom chilly virgin justice had as a worthy servant; but
jealous, hatefully-named Fate snatched him quickly, <supplied cert="low" reason="explanation">he who was</supplied>
splendid <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
               <seg cert="low">taking away</seg>.</ab>
         </div>
